Installation instructions

mkdir /var/cache/ansible_logs
chmod 770 /var/cache/ansible_logs
chown root:ansible_users /var/cache/ansible_logs

copy sqlite_logger.py into callback_plugins in the directory containing your ansible.cfg

#ansible.cfg 
[defaults]
#interpreter_python = auto_silent
callbacks_enabled = sqlite_logger
callback_plugins = ./callback_plugins

Run the python flask app in the webserver of your choice.  
Try it first with python3 app.py
